oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Jones, Grandpa, 1913-1998; Shepard, Jean, 1933-2016; Osborne Brothers; Tubb, Justin; Wood, Del; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and black on brown) announcing Grandpa Jones, Jean Shepard, Osborne Brothers, Justin Tubb, and Del Wood at the Tennessee Wesleyan College Auditorium on October 10. Poster features metal photoplates of Grandpa Jones, Jean Shepard, the Osborne Brothers, Justin Tubb, and Del Wood. To see the business record associated with this poster, visit https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/52025/
